    "body": "This PR adds an \"external URL\" icon after external urls. See example screenshots below.\r\n\r\nI can imagine some might not like it because it can be a bit noisy. I'll let the maintainers decide.\r\n\r\nFiltering out certain elements is also definitely possible, I already excluded buttons (`.btn`).\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1853\" height=\"1086\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dd05bd40-323e-4e25-b0a9-3c3bb22da479\" />\r\n<img width=\"1848\" height=\"1083\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/baa6adc0-bb05-49e8-8951-9024a2476c78\" />\r\n<img width=\"1852\" height=\"1084\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/352d0a57-42b7-4b75-bd97-f2685fae393c\" />\r\n\r\n",
